Climobots Sense Base v1
========================

An Arduino UNO shield with multiple enviromental sensors and a SD card.
Developed by Angela Gabereau at Santa Elena, Colombia

-------
Sensors
-------


GPS
-------
Pin 8, Digital, Software Serial TX
Pin 9, Digital, Software Serial RX

Adafruit GPD Breakout v3
modules using MTK3329/MTK3339 driver 
http://www.adafruit.com/products/746

Library: Adafruit-GPS-Library

Barometric Pressure
-------
Pin
BMP180 Presure Sensor

Library: Adafruit_BMP085_U

Gas
-------
Pin 0, Analog

n/a
I used the gas sensor that Platohedro had.  
I did not note the make/model


Soil
-------
Pin 2, Analog

Original: n/a
I used the soil sensor that Platohedro had.  
I did not note the make/model

Current: Grove Moisture Sensor


Sound
-------
Pin 3, Analog

DFRobot Analog Sound Sensor V2



Temperature & Humidity (DHT)
-------
Pin 2, Digital

DFRobot Temperature & Humidity V2
https://www.dfrobot.com/wiki/index.php/DHT11_Temperature_and_Humidity_Sensor_V2_SKU:_DFR0067

Current: Adafruit DHT Library
https://github.com/adafruit/DHT-sensor-library
http://playground.arduino.cc/Main/DHTLib, contains basic info and alternatives

Other options:
Smaller Footprint, for just DHT11
http://playground.arduino.cc/Main/DHT11Lib


Light
-------
Pin 1, Analog

Photo Resistor


